<style>
  body {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: #F2EAD3;
    color: #222222;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  #container {
    max-width: 560px;
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Archivo Black', 'Arial Black', sans-serif;
    font-size: 6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .intro p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    color: #666666;
  }

  .faq-item {
    margin: 0.9rem 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .faq-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 2px;
    height: 100%;
    background: #B7A878;
    transform: scaleY(0);
    transform-origin: top;
    transition: transform 0.45s ease;
    transition-delay: 0s;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .faq-item.opening::before,
  .faq-item.open::before {
    transform: scaleY(1);
    transition-delay: 0.32s;
  }

  .faq-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.6s ease;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .faq-header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 2px;
    background: #B7A878;
    transform: translateX(0);
    opacity: 1;
    transition: transform 0.32s ease, opacity 0.32s ease;
  }

  .faq-item.opening .faq-header::before,
  .faq-item.open .faq-header::before {
    transform: translateX(-100%);
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .faq-header:hover {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .faq-item.open .faq-header {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    padding-bottom: 0.7rem;
  }

  .faq-header h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0;
    color: #222222;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .faq-arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    margin-left: 0.75rem;
    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .faq-arrow::after {
    content: '';
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-right: 2px solid #222222;
    border-top: 2px solid #222222;
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .faq-item.open .faq-arrow {
    transform: rotate(90deg);
  }

  .faq-content {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.6s ease;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .faq-item.open .faq-content {
    max-height: 500px;
  }

  .faq-content p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.1rem 1rem;
    color: #555555;
  }

  #btn {
    border: 1.5px dashed #241D16;
    background: #F2EAD3;
    color: #241D16;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.75rem 0.6rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    min-width: 6rem;
    transition: background 0.14s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: -1rem;
  }

  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    body {
      background: #0f0f0f;
      color: #f5f5f5;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #f5f5f5;
    }

    .intro p {
      color: #b0b0b0;
    }

    .faq-header {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }

    .faq-header:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }

    .faq-header h3 {
      color: #f5f5f5;
    }

    .faq-arrow::after {
      border-right-color: #f5f5f5;
      border-top-color: #f5f5f5;
    }

    .faq-header::before {
      background: #B7A878;
    }

    .faq-item::before {
      background: #B7A878;
    }

    .faq-item.open .faq-content {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }

    .faq-content p {
      color: #a0a0a0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }

    #container {
      padding: 0;
    }

    .faq-header {
      padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
    }

    .faq-content p {
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem 0.95rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<div id="container">
  <h1>Issued</h1>
  
  <div class="intro">
    <p>Get them questions ready, cuz i'm ready!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <h3>How do I create a design?</h3>
      <div class="faq-arrow"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-content">
      <p>Using a coding language like HTML and CSS to create your design.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <h3>What are the design requirements?</h3>
      <div class="faq-arrow"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-content">
      <p>Designs must be the best you can create and must be appropriate! Also please don't submit designs made in software such as Photoshop or Illustrator.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <h3>How does the ordering process work?</h3>
      <div class="faq-arrow"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-content">
      <p>You can order your design or potentially someone else's design, in exchange for <%= ENV.fetch('CURRENCY_NAME', 'Currency') %> earned from making your own designs.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <h3>Can I edit my design after submission?</h3>
      <div class="faq-arrow"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-content">
      <p>To do so ensure you haven't submitted your design for fufillment and contact <a href="https://hackclub.slack.com/team/U078KKF3R1Q">me</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <h3>Is this free?</h3>
      <div class="faq-arrow"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-content">
      <p>Yes, it is free but only for teenagers 13-18.</p>
      <button id="btn" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;" onclick="window.location.href='https://hackclub.com/'">
        Join Hack Club
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <h3>How does fufillment work?</h3>
      <div class="faq-arrow"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-content">
      <p>We are currently deciding whether to have everything quality checked before sending or sending direct to you, the former may induce customs.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <h3>Anything else?</h3>
      <div class="faq-arrow"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-content">
      <button id="btn" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;" onclick="window.location.href='https://issued.fillout.com/faq'">
        Create a new Question
      </button>
      <%# <p>Or wait for our faq system to be made available.</p> %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  const openTimers = new WeakMap();

  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(item => {
    const header = item.querySelector('.faq-header');

    header.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const existingTimer = openTimers.get(item);
      if (existingTimer) {
        clearTimeout(existingTimer);
        openTimers.delete(item);
      }

      if (item.classList.contains('open') || item.classList.contains('opening')) {
        item.classList.remove('open', 'opening');
        return;
      }

      item.classList.add('opening');

      const timer = setTimeout(() => {
        item.classList.add('open');
        item.classList.remove('opening');
        openTimers.delete(item);
      }, 320);

      openTimers.set(item, timer);
    });
  });
</script>
